{"word":"G2477 - ἱστορέω - historéō - his-tor-eh'-o - See","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἱστορέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">historéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">his-tor-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">See</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கண்டுகொள்"},{"paragraph":"1. to inquire into, examine, investigate"},{"paragraph":"2. to find out, learn, by inquiry"},{"paragraph":"3. to gain knowledge of by visiting"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a derivative of <a href=\"#/G1492 - εἴδω - eídō - i'-do/1492\">G1492</a>; to <i>be knowing</i> (<i>learned</i>), that is, (by implication) to <i>visit</i> for information (<i>interview</i>): - see.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}